name: Mellow Bananas #001
description:
The first Airdrop NFT for Mellow Monkey Holders!

Sent out to holders of the first 116 Mellow Monkeys.



'Mellow Monkeys' is a pixel art NFT Collectibles project available on Hicetnunc. 

Mellow Monkeys are 1/1, unique and hand drawn.

There are a total of 500 monkeys waiting to be collected!
